raw_data.title: 360 Assessment: The Leadership Circle
raw_data.description: The Leadership Circle Profile (LCP) is a breakthrough 360-degree profile. It is the first to connect a well-researched battery of competencies with the underlying and motivating habits of thought. It reveals the relationship between patterns of action and internal assumptions that drive behavior. Ultimately, LCP goes to the source of behavior to get greater leverage on change. Furthermore, unlike most profiles that take hours to interpret, LCP integrates all this information in a way that brings the key issues to the surface instantly.
